{"tid":1484440,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府：集會口號針對警方感遺憾，籲市民向暴力說不 --- 政府又講廢話，和理非係時候再發起三罷!!!","createTime":"2019-08-18T14:42:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:31:42.000Z","uid":139667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f2c800222faa2dbbb2938ad3ebc37bce82d3f44e","tid":1484440,"uid":139667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"【22:18】政府發言人表示，雖然集會期間大致和平，但由於參與者佔用了港島多條主要幹道，路面交通大受影響，對市民造成不便。發言人重申，目前最重要的是要盡快回復社會秩序；當一切平靜之後，政府會與市民展開真誠對話，致力修補撕裂，重建社會和諧。<br />\n<br />\n【15:25】民陣今午（18日）2時發起「止黑暴，制警亂」維園集會，政府於2時18分發聲明，對有團體今日以針對警方的口號舉行集會表示遺憾，指出去年香港錄得的整體罪案數字是自1974年以來最低，強調在過去兩個多月，警方一直以容忍態度處理激進和暴力示威者的違法事件，特區政府會全力支持警方嚴正執法。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，香港向來是十分安全的城市，2018年錄得的整體罪案數字是54225宗，數字是自1974年以來最低。而警隊在2018年進行的服務滿意程度調查和公眾意見調查顯示，84%受訪者對警隊整體服務表現感到「非常滿意」或「頗滿意」，為2000年推行警隊服務滿意程度調查以來最高的百分比。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190818/s00001/1566111388727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190818%2Fs00001%2F1566111388727&d=Xp%2F1NtumznDfUUYtKZVD8sdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=f764bcca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190818%2Fs00001%2F1566111388727&h=7996326e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190818/s00001/1566111388727</a><br />\n<br />\n今日好感動，818 証明左香港人唔係金魚，而且核爆都唔會同勇武割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學界已經Plan 緊九月份罷課抗議政府完全無視莫視民間的訴求，今次又點可以少左我地果份??<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故此我強烈建議，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">八月尾/九月頭發起第二次三罷，但係今次要升級到兩日</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4ba0de5071b2b6503b3d7f425dbac2342aa0718f","tid":1484440,"uid":139667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:05:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"76e7148d94f33848f6223d3874c2b2697f643358","tid":1484440,"uid":306045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:32:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />罷定唔罷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【真係攬炒咩】升級大三罷，九月百萬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1481216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1481216</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WcAUV1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWcAUV1N.jpg&h=b7391bad&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k1BXTOs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk1BXTOs.jpg&h=c19a5d2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eL552GO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeL552GO.jpg&h=8908370c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9gQumO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9gQumO.jpg&h=6c8b424d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U3gXTOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU3gXTOt.jpg&h=4bdc5ca1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Kg3O0tu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKg3O0tu.jpg&h=2fb4220a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mJNPKU9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmJNPKU9.jpg&h=8cbab5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wzsDDfa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwzsDDfa.jpg&h=cb9b7147&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sDtGA1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.k